data.description: Two Houses on One Acre. The Front House has 2 Bedrooms. One Bedroomhas its own full bath Appx 1,605 Sq Ft. There is a second 3/4 bathroom off the hallway.As you walk in the front door, there is a large living room open tothe kitchen and dining area. From the living room, you enter a largeopen family room. The family room has sliding glass doors leading tothe back yard porch area and back yard. There is a two-car attachedgarage that has a cement driveway with parking for several vehicles.The front of the house has a porch that stretches from on end of thehouse to the other side of the house. There are several trees and agrass area at the front of the house. From the front of the house,there is a rock driveway leading to the rear of the house. The rear ofthe house has an enclosed porch area with a grass area and sewerhookup for an RV.From the back yard area there is a second home that is separate fromthe front house with its own driveway, septic, electric, gas (needs tobe replaced), fenced and separated by evergreen plants. The rear househas a large open room, with a kitchen area, full bath, bedroom, andlarge closet. Appx 920 Sq Ft. The backdoor opens into an enclosed porch area, carport,and garage. There are two fenced areas for animals.This is part of Hesperia where the lots are one acre or more and theZoning  Allows for parking of Commercial Vehicles (Big Rigs, 18Wheelers); Second Dwelling Units; Guest House; Home Occupation;Accessory Buildings and Structures; Buildings or Structures to storeAgricultural Vehicles; Food and Equipment (Barn or out buildings);Buildings or Structures to keep Animals (Stable, Corral, Pen or Coop);Small Livestock: Horses, Mules, Donkeys, Lamas, Fowl and Cattle.
